   "\"\<OperatorVectorRepresentation[op,OperatorBasis->basis] derives the \
vector representation of an operator in a given operator basis.The vector \
representation of an operator Q is given by {(B1|Q),(B2|Q)..} where {|B1), \
|B2)..} are the basis operators.\>\""}], ";"}]], "Input",
