IntermediateOperatorBasis settings that include this basis.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 InitializationGroup->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.439434449367018*^9, 3.439434470028729*^9}, {
  3.439434525648065*^9, 3.4394345265806932`*^9}, {3.699893599761632*^9, 
