   3.531927266549382*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"249c2a98-4d4e-473a-a550-\
221c2f6da218"],

Cell["\<\
Superoperator converts a superoperator expression into the Superoperator[..] \
form which either contains the explicit matrix representation in a given \
operator basis, or as a CommutationSuperoperator of an operator, expressed as \
a matrix in a given basis. The options to Superoperator may specify the \
SuperoperatorType, which may be deduced automatically from the form of the \
superoperator matrix representation, or from the contained operator, in the \
case of a CommutationSuperoperator.\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.583428957871188*^9, 
  3.5834290878728952`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b49380d2-d505-4310-8682-\
8149993a4049"],

