Cell["\<\
Only determine the SuperoperatorType if the matrix is numeric, and the \
dimension is not too large - or if it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s a \
CommutationSuperoperator\
\>", "Text",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5834321822769756`*^9, 3.583432195403837*^9}, {
