Cell["\<\
detect a conflict between the Assumptions and a determined OperatorType, and \
issue a warning if necessary\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 InitializationCell->True,
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.502517743059229*^9, 3.502517750937834*^9}, {
  3.586254495213749*^9, 3.586254507924302*^9}, {3.586255024399542*^9, 
